Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:09.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same power, the same voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's uncanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That power interests me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your very presence disgusts me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time I ended this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Happy's Fairy Tail Lectures!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:04.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll be teaching you about \NCarla and myself's homeland, Edolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world we live in is called "Earthland"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas is a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In Edolas, magic power is a limited \Nresource that will one day be used up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, King Faust
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:21.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,used the hyperspace magic Anima to \Nabsorb magic power from Earthland!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild and people from Magnolia \Nwere turned into a lacrima,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're all fighting \Nto return them to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, there's a separate set \Nof Natsu and the others in Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Erza in Edolas is our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:36.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't rest easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there you have it. Let's \Nget back to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, bow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that one of the Fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a human, a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fallen one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,brought a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Extalia is in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Doomsday Dragon Chain Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nady-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:54.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fallen and Humans are \Nforbidden from entering Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you people value your lives, then listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Nichiya-san and the rest of \Nthe guards go that were chasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been turned into a \Nlacrima by the Royal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Extalia's Royal Guard done in by some humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect us to believe \Nsomething as silly as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:33.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! The Royal Army \Nwill be attacking here shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Queen will blow them \Nall away with her magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, if you don't escape, \Nyou'll all be in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know how \Npowerful our Queen is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Exceeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not like you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, Human! Get out, Fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the blessed land \Nof our Queen, Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't going to lose to some humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as our Queen is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:24.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate humans that much, \Ndo with me what you must!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Carla is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:32.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what she says, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! Get out! Get out! Get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unarmed, you can stop my iron-hard sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland magic is full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to break it to you, but an Iron \NDragon's iron isn't normal iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, aren't you one of the cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you working for the Royal Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an Exceed like me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would... you like a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have forsaken my homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That fake country!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake country...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An outcast, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it. Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your style!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make this guy my cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Buster Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But first I gotta show you \Nwhich one of us is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:44.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think his switch just flipped on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be outdone by Salamander \Nor that little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel's looking scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it's gotta be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel... Are you forgetting why \Nwe're here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an Ice Maker Magic wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make as many keys as I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:55.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally caught up to the bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to leave him to me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You chinny bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Can't you see what I have in my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuck? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boobs are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Natsu... We can use this key!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use it to save all of our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their plan was to use the Dragon Chain cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to pull the lacrima island \Nand ram it into Extalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we crash the Dragon Chain Cannon, \Ninfused with Dragon Slayer magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,directly into the lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can return everyone to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:55.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I don't get it, but I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Chain Cannon seems to be up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to enter the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we just bust our way in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use magic now, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:20.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some kind of "Wizard Canceler" \Ndevice that makes it so magic won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't know until we try, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need a plan, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:40.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... That's the Edolas's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:49.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Erza... lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you well, Captain Knightwalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where did you get those wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And those two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to the Dragon Chain Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Key?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is His Highness inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An eternity of magic, right before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you call out to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plotting something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the latest information... if I'm \Ngoing to convince everyone, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Convince us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They heard you had something to \Nsay, Lucy-san, so they're uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:24.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After meeting those guys from the other \Nworld, Lucy's been more uptight than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That'd scare anyone, for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bunch of goddamn scaredy-cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't harmonize!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:55.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, is it true you bring the key with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was destroyed, but do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can make a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An Earthland wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of the Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have something to do with the \Ndisappearance of the lacrima in the public square?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate the Dragon Chain Cannon immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, Ice Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate the Dragon Chain Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dragon Chain Cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a whole lot different than I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On a much bigger scale, for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Earthland magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why is he naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should charge admission for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash the Dragon Chain Cannon \Nstraight into the lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That way we can save all our friends, \Nand everyone from Magnolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The castle is transforming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Chain Cannon has been activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like the Gildarts Shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What insane idiot came up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I change the aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Dragon Chain Cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are proceeding \Nfaster than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! I must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:36.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What treachery is this, Erza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Erza Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland's Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. Your quick \Nthinking helped us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was plan D! D for Dupe the Dolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim the Dragon Chain Cannon at the lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a hostage? That's low!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:42.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do whatever it takes \Nto save our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:44.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and do it, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it! Our Highness is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire it, in order to destroy the Exceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Readjust the aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change it to hit the giant lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to throw away \Nan eternity of magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knightwalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness has been freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, revert the aim back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knightwalker, you're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over yet, Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Chain Cannon has connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Something huge has stuck on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grappling complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ram it into Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You turned into a giant monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your blabbing and get on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that girl ride a Legion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This Legion is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but we have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legion Squad of the Second \NMagic Regiment, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Droma Anim ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's a forbidden craft...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strictly forbidden under the \NCharter of the Kingdom, Article 23!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our army's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:22:01.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will ram this lacrima into Extalia, \Nand they will annihilate each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do something so horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:21.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:57.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stop it, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:24:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna let a single person in Fairy \NTail or a single Exceed be sacrificed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:08.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I found an extremely \Nrare fish the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go catch it next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:11.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:14.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that time we \Nall went to the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Boy Back Then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying we have to go right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:21.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The early worm catches the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}so{\i0} not the time.
